1
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,599
What are you doing?

2
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,319
Close your eyes.

3
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:53,760
Do it now.

4
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,159
Take a deep breath.

5
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,080
Listen.

6
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,240
What can you hear?

7
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:42,960
The world

8
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,000
has all kinds of sounds every day.

9
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,120
Even if you cover your ears,

10
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,240
they still find their way in.

11
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,479
But they're like clouds in the sky,

12
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:54,599
a gust of wind

13
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,599
and they'll clear away,

14
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,319
and the sky will turn bright again.

15
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,120
Ye,

16
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,479
adult matters

17
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:08,520
are not your fault.

18
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:22,879
The Ye I know

19
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,319
is upright

20
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,199
and fearless.

21
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:38,560
Thank you.

22
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:43,120
You're right.

23
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:44,960
This little thing

24
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,400
can't beat me.

25
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:49,039
All rumors

26
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,080
will fall apart on their own.

27
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:53,879
Of course.

28
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:00,840
Eat up.

29
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,319
Eat.

30
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,319
Finish and I'll take you somewhere.

31
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,319
Where?

32
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,199
You'll see.

33
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:53,839
What's wrong?

34
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,000
Why did you say

35
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,600
that Qing Ye bullied me and Li Wenhui?

36
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,199
I was just standing up for you.

37
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:04,759
I only used
the wrong word.

38
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,040
And you didn't exactly

39
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,120
come out ahead anyway.

40
00:05:08,639 --> 00:05:10,120
Should I have said

41
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:10,959
you bullied her instead?

42
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,920
We were helping you.

43
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,160
I never asked you to.

44
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:16,519
What do you mean?

45
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,680
Trying to dump the blame

46
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:19,040
on me now?

47
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,199
Fang Lei.

48
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:23,399
How can you think that of me?

49
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,800
I only told you the truth

50
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:25,959
because I trusted you most.

51
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,480
You think I'm stupid?

52
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,800
I know

53
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:30,319
that post was you.

54
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,399
What does that have to do with me?

55
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,680
Then you must've forgotten

56
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,720
the teddy bear on your forum avatar

57
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,319
was a gift from me.

58
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,319
You saw wrong.

59
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,120
How could it be me?

60
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,680
Don't worry.

61
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,680
I won't tell anyone.

62
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:52,319
But this is the last thing
I'll do for you.

63
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:55,600
From now on,

64
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,199
I don't have a friend like you.

65
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:11,720
With the Sea Goddess as witness,

66
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,000
it will carry

67
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,160
your thoughts of your mother

68
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,480
on the wind.

69
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:17,600
Old-fashioned it is,

70
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,759
but thanks anyway.

71
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,040
Do you think

72
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,920
Mom will receive this lantern?

73
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:51,160
Probably not.

74
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,399
Then why did you sound so sure

75
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:56,160
about the Sea Goddess as witness?

76
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:58,040
That was just what I hoped.

77
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,480
In reality, one is in the sky,

78
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:01,600
the other in the sea,

79
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:03,360
probably not the same system.

80
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,360
Then what if we ignore all that?

81
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,480
Still no.

82
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,319
It won't fly for long

83
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,079
before it falls.

84
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:15,920
Can't you

85
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,199
be a bit more romantic?

86
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:22,040
Even if she doesn't receive the lantern,

87
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:23,480
she will

88
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,240
receive your thoughts.

89
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,319
Your longing for your mother

90
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,879
will cross the sea

91
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,199
and be carried by time.

92
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,319
Who taught you

93
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,040
to talk like that?

94
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:38,600
A philosopher,

95
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:39,639
Zhou Guimei.

96
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:52,439
[Hello?]

97
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:54,040
Hello.

98
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,000
Is Qing Ye

99
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:58,160
doing alright?

100
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,040
[She's fine.]
Good.

101
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,920
I'll help you

102
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:03,759
set up another time
with Mr. Ye.

103
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:05,600
[Thanks.]

104
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,680
"Thanks."

105
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,840
Have some watermelon.

106
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,480
It's really sweet.

107
00:08:57,799 --> 00:08:58,919
Finish it and forget everything.

108
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:00,600
Get a good night's sleep.

109
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,840
Tomorrow it'll all be over.

110
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,639
It's not over yet.

111
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,799
If dealing with rumors means

112
00:09:12,039 --> 00:09:13,519
waiting for the liar to shut up,

113
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:15,519
that's not fair.

114
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,759
What do you want to do?

115
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,879
I want an eye for an eye.

116
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,559
Alright.

117
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:28,480
Need my help?

118
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:29,840
No.

119
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:32,320
I'll bring this

120
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:33,399
to an end myself.

121
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,120
If you need help,

122
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,039
just say it anytime.

123
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,320
I'm heading to Shunyi.

124
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,159
Good night.

125
00:09:44,559 --> 00:09:45,200
Good night.

126
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,039
Auntie,

127
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:36,320
where's Wu?

128
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,919
He rushed off to Shunyi

129
00:12:37,919 --> 00:12:38,960
early in the morning,

130
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,960
like something urgent came up.

131
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:03,399
[The clothes are clean,]

132
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:05,360
[with a scent of sunshine.]

133
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:10,399
[It's a nice sunny day today.]

134
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:36,759
Xia Luodi.

135
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,080
Xia Luodi, you belong on the ground.

136
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,200
What, aiming for the heavens now?

137
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,559
That's your ID, right?

138
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,639
I don't know what you're talking about.

139
00:13:43,919 --> 00:13:44,799
I didn't post
those rumor threads.

140
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:47,320
Did I say it was you?

141
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:48,919
You're pretty self-aware.

142
00:13:51,519 --> 00:13:53,000
Don't accuse people randomly.

143
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,320
That teddy bear

144
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,320
on your avatar,

145
00:13:57,559 --> 00:13:59,039
why isn't it there today?

146
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,039
Does what I hang
concern you?

147
00:14:02,559 --> 00:14:03,480
Tough mouth.

148
00:14:04,399 --> 00:14:05,679
That's basically

149
00:14:05,919 --> 00:14:07,360
"Too guilty to deny it.'

150
00:14:13,399 --> 00:14:14,759
Don't think Xing Wu backing you up

151
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,320
means you can slander people.

152
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,600
I'm not like you.

153
00:14:22,519 --> 00:14:23,320
I don't play dirty tricks

154
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,600
behind people's backs.

155
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,080
If you don't like me
and wanna beat me,

156
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,320
then do it properly,

157
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,240
let's compete in the next exam.

158
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,159
Fine.

159
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,039
Let everyone see

160
00:14:36,399 --> 00:14:37,759
who's got real ability

161
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:39,919
and who's just bluffing.

162
00:14:40,559 --> 00:14:41,080
Deal.

163
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,759
You set the bet.

164
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,879
Loser runs ten laps.

165
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:51,080
Ten laps?

166
00:14:53,759 --> 00:14:55,039
Don't dare?

167
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:57,840
20 laps then.

168
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,000
- 20 laps!
- Oh my!

169
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,000
Go big or don't go.

170
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:03,840
Deal.

171
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,039
It's set.

172
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:09,519
Not finished yet?

173
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,240
Far from it.

174
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,039
What do you want?

175
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:24,759
Want you to delete some posts.

176
00:15:25,879 --> 00:15:26,679
Not urgent, 1,000.

177
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:27,759
Express, 1,500.

178
00:15:28,559 --> 00:15:30,360
I'll give you 2,000. Do it fast.

179
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,120
It's about Qing Ye.

180
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,840
What's your relationship with her?

181
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,240
Coming here just to help her delete posts?

182
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,759
I'm her classmate.

183
00:15:42,639 --> 00:15:44,039
I just think she's a good person.

184
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,159
I don't want her bullied
or dragged through rumors

185
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:46,759
at school.

186
00:15:47,759 --> 00:15:48,320
So,

187
00:15:48,679 --> 00:15:49,399
can you do it or not?

188
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:51,799
I won't take this job.
I'll pay more.

189
00:15:52,799 --> 00:15:54,320
Even that won't get me to take it.

190
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,360
Aren't you her cousin?

191
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,519
You won't even help her out?

192
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:03,320
Not that I won't help.

193
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,600
It's just not your place.

194
00:16:08,039 --> 00:16:09,080
Your brother told me to give this to you.

195
00:16:10,039 --> 00:16:10,759
Sorry for the trouble.

196
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,519
Me and your brother, though

197
00:16:14,559 --> 00:16:15,639
met in prison,

198
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:17,360
but he looked out for me.

199
00:16:17,639 --> 00:16:19,200
We're life-and-death brothers.

200
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,000
Ping's sister is my sister.

201
00:16:22,559 --> 00:16:23,720
No need to be so formal.

202
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:27,919
He…

203
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:29,399
asked me to pass a message.

204
00:16:31,039 --> 00:16:32,559
He's been waiting for you to visit.

205
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,320
If you're too busy,
just write a letter.

206
00:16:35,919 --> 00:16:37,039
He's not my brother.

207
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,399
If he hadn't gone to prison,

208
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,360
I wouldn't be living

209
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,679
under someone else's roof,

210
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:43,879
getting side-eyes,

211
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:45,759
and even being bullied at school.

212
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:47,679
What's going on?

213
00:16:48,159 --> 00:16:49,000
Who bullied you?

214
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:18,319
[If you don't want your brother's past]
[to get out,]

215
00:17:19,799 --> 00:17:21,119
[stay away from Qing Ye.]

216
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:24,160
Happy now?

217
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,039
Uncle, you're back.

218
00:17:28,359 --> 00:17:29,319
What are you doing?

219
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,839
Get back to work!

220
00:17:34,839 --> 00:17:35,759
Did you forget something?

221
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,039
That's all the money?

222
00:17:54,319 --> 00:17:54,839
Come on,

223
00:17:55,039 --> 00:17:57,079
I'll take you out tomorrow.

224
00:18:34,039 --> 00:18:34,839
Ye,

225
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:36,079
did you see it?

226
00:18:37,599 --> 00:18:38,240
See what?
This.

227
00:18:53,359 --> 00:18:54,880
Who posted this?

228
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,079
No idea.

229
00:18:59,319 --> 00:18:59,920
Ye.

230
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,319
Did you see it?

231
00:19:09,559 --> 00:19:10,400
You posted this?

232
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:11,680
Not me.

233
00:19:12,519 --> 00:19:13,880
I don't have the right to do that.

234
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:15,440
I'd like to help you.

235
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:16,880
But your brother said

236
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:18,319
it's not my place.

237
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,000
It's Wu.

238
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:38,359
[Did you post the apology?]

239
00:19:39,039 --> 00:19:39,640
[No.]

240
00:19:42,319 --> 00:19:44,559
[Some people just won't admit it.]

241
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:51,640
Wu,

242
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,559
you've seemed

243
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:55,519
a bit off lately.

244
00:19:59,319 --> 00:20:00,440
You've been

245
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:01,440
pretty paranoid.

246
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:03,759
Stop staring at me.

247
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,400
Did you see the post?

248
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,480
She already clarified it.

249
00:20:19,319 --> 00:20:20,319
I saw it.

250
00:20:20,359 --> 00:20:22,319
Who knows if it's true?

251
00:20:22,559 --> 00:20:23,440
Listen…

252
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:27,839
People from big cities are sharp,

253
00:20:28,039 --> 00:20:29,000
better keep your distance.

254
00:20:31,519 --> 00:20:32,599
What class today?

255
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:35,039
Stop gossiping.

256
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:36,119
What, forget when you

257
00:20:36,119 --> 00:20:37,160
running your mouth about others?

258
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,240
Getting bold now.

259
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,319
Wait, aren't they…

260
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:51,559
Take it.

261
00:20:52,799 --> 00:20:53,519
What for?

262
00:20:54,759 --> 00:20:55,880
At the cafeteria before,

263
00:20:56,039 --> 00:20:57,240
Cao Fan said you bullied me,

264
00:20:58,079 --> 00:20:59,519
I didn't explain it well.

265
00:21:00,359 --> 00:21:01,119
So this is…

266
00:21:04,079 --> 00:21:05,759
Are you apologizing to me?

267
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:09,319
You really talk
that bluntly?

268
00:21:10,319 --> 00:21:11,519
No tact at all.

269
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:15,319
I'm just blunt.

270
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:17,160
I don't sugarcoat things.

271
00:21:20,599 --> 00:21:21,240
Alright.

272
00:21:21,319 --> 00:21:22,319
I admit it I'm apologizing.

273
00:21:22,359 --> 00:21:23,359
I messed up sorry,

274
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,000
I own it.

275
00:21:25,759 --> 00:21:26,759
But that doesn't mean

276
00:21:27,559 --> 00:21:28,720
I wanna be friends with you.

277
00:21:31,359 --> 00:21:32,240
What's so funny?

278
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:33,799
Stop laughing.

279
00:21:33,799 --> 00:21:35,559
I'm laughing because
you're pretty interesting.

280
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:36,680
Do people here

281
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:37,759
all like
saying one thing and meaning another?

282
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,000
Saying one thing and meaning another?

283
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,799
I don't do that.

284
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:46,240
I'd like to know

285
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:48,200
who's being two-faced.

286
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:49,839
Tell me.

287
00:21:51,759 --> 00:21:52,480
Didn't expect that, right?

288
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:53,960
Yeah, I didn't.

289
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:00,640
Just now…

290
00:22:35,279 --> 00:22:36,960
[Auntie, I've got a mock exam today.]

291
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,240
[I'm off to school.]

292
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:46,640
Qing Ye?

293
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,119
I'm not.

294
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,079
Who are you?

